Source will be more than half filled and target will be less than half filled.
Items from source are copied to target unitl source become at least half full.
After : if target < source : leftSibling, using forward iterator
After : if target > source : rightSibling, using backward iterator
Merge is given preference over redistribution. Redistribution happens only when
both siblings are more than half filled.

When T> S: You transfer cells from source to tragte, until half +1, you make the
